#

Shrimp Tacos with Corn Tortillas

20 min
$15
300 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Shellfish

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeSeafoodHigh-Protein

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Main

Tags:

QuickHealthyTacosSeafood

Description

Quick and zesty shrimp tacos wrapped in soft corn tortillas, topped with fresh ingredients for a delightful meal.

Ingredients

  • shrimp (peeled and deveined): 1 pound
  • corn tortillas: 8
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • garlic (minced): 2 cloves
  • cilantro (chopped): 1/4 cup
  • lime (juiced): 1
  • salt: to taste
  • cabbage (shredded): 1 cup
  • avocado (sliced): 1
  • sour cream or greek yogurt (optional): 1/2 cup
